rComments: Horribly bad. Consistently gets questions wrong. Can be fun to sit in class with book and correct every error. His voice is 95% Charlie Brown's Teacher's voice. Just don't sign up for this section. Srsly.

Absolutely the worst 210 professor ever. Avoid at all costs. Switch to another professor or just go to another session. He will often make mistakes and confuse the class. In addition, he only does questions from the text and is barely audible.

Bring a pillow, or, switch to one of the other concurrent 210 lectures. The only benefit of this guy is his lecture notes. He uploads his lectures online and those will sometimes present an easier-to-comprehend display of the course material.
